  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca \u2018\u2018\u0d85\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0d9c\u0dbd\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dd2\u2018\u2018",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ranil \"saves His Excellency\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe said in a special statement after taking the oath that the use of the word His Excellency in front of the name of the President will be prohibited.",
        "Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe also mentioned that the presidential flag will be abolished and a country should have only one flag.",
        "The President also said that a nation should move forward from the shadow of one flag and said that he will work for the full implementation of the Nineteenth Amendment to the Constitution."
      ],
